name.ja: アドバンス・インパクト

requirement.en: You have no monsters on your field.

effect.en: Choose 1 face-up monster on your opponent's field, and send monsters from your hand to the Graveyard whose total Levels equal the chosen monster's Level. This turn, if you would Tribute Summon a monster, you can Tribute the chosen opponent's face-up monster instead of 1 monster on your field.
